      <profileDesc>
         <abstract><p>The <foreign xml:lang="gez">Maṣḥafa Henok</foreign> is a Jewish apocalypse preserved only in Gǝʿǝz.
         The original language of the work seems to have been Aramaic. There are fragments of a Greek version, which have been used
         by the Ethiopic translator as a Vorlage.
            <bibl><ptr target="bm:Uhlig2005EAEEnoch"/></bibl></p></abstract>
